<li id="cite_note-Sta2013-7"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Sta2013_7-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Sta2013_7-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Sta2013_7-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Sta2013_7-3"><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation journal">Stahl, M; Mariette, C; Haustermans, K; Cervantes, A; Arnold, D; ESMO Guidelines Working, Group (Oct 2013). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://annonc.oxfordjournals.org/content/24/suppl_6/vi51.full">"Oesophageal cancer: ESMO Clinical Practice Guidelines for diagnosis, treatment and follow-up."</a>. <i>Annals of oncology&#160;: official journal of the European Society for Medical Oncology / ESMO</i>. 24 Suppl 6: vi51–6. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//dx.doi.org/10.1093%2Fannonc%2Fmdt342">10.1093/annonc/mdt342</a>. <a href="/wiki/PubMed_Identifier" title="PubMed Identifier" class="mw-redirect">PMID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24078662">24078662</a>.</span><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AEsophageal+cancer&amp;rft.atitle=Oesophageal+cancer%3A+ESMO+Clinical+Practice+Guidelines+for+diagnosis%2C+treatment+and+follow-up.&amp;rft.au=Arnold%2C+D&amp;rft.au=Cervantes%2C+A&amp;rft.au=ESMO+Guidelines+Working%2C+Group&amp;rft.aufirst=M&amp;rft.au=Haustermans%2C+K&amp;rft.aulast=Stahl&amp;rft.au=Mariette%2C+C&amp;rft.au=Stahl%2C+M&amp;rft.date=Oct+2013&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fannonc.oxfordjournals.org%2Fcontent%2F24%2Fsuppl_6%2Fvi51.full&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1093%2Fannonc%2Fmdt342&amp;rft_id=info%3Apmid%2F24078662&amp;rft.jtitle=Annals+of+oncology+%3A+official+journal+of+the+European+Society+for+Medical+Oncology+%2F+ESMO&amp;rft.pages=vi51-6&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3A